{
  "stem": "3331.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my father promised him that he will be-- we call it in Jewish, we call kest.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It means the daughter is marrying somebody and we take him in for a year to eat, to live, and we will support him.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This was kest.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he came in for a year and we gave him an apartment in our house on the second floor.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the end was that he was in this place for 22 years.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He never moved out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He never paid rent.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He never paid for, for food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because, in a store like this, he-- they took anything they wanted.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were very happy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was set.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother was happy with it, my father was happy with this arrangements.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had enough.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So all the sisters, after they married, they still were connected with our business.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were a lot of incidents.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For instance, our town was distinguished to have a pogrom.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not every town was so lucky to have a pogrom, but our town had a pogrom.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When the Poles gained their independence in 1918 in the Versailles Treaty-- so after 150 years, under occupation of Russia, Austria, and Germany, so they wanted to celebrate.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "After all, to have independence is not every day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So what is there a better way then to celebrate than to have a pogrom.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Naturally, not a big pogrom, because it was a small town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "To have a small pogrom.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the whole town was destroyed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After three days, they didn't have any more to rob, to plunder, so they went away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, nevertheless, nine Jews were, were killed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So this was the beginning of the celebration of having an independent Poland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I remember the exact day.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
